channel.title: Hamachi Launching
channel.description: Whenever I try to launch Hamachi, Version 1.0.1.4, it always pops up a box that says, "Version 1.0.1.4 detected, would you like to update." If I click yes, it doesn't really update, because when I try to run it again it does the same thing. If I click no, then it exits me out and won't load. WTH?
